  QL_BalladOfHeroes_Step02:
    contents:
      - text: "The One-Hit Obliterator, as the name suggests,\ncan defeat enemies in one-hit. However,\nthe wielder will also be defeated in one hit.\nDefeat the monsters at the locations marked\non the map within the Great Plateau.\n\nIf you wish to quit this trial, simply leave the\nGreat Plateau. The weapon will leave your\nhands and return to the Shrine of Resurrection.\n\nThere are "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: four
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: " monster bases remaining."
